==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Terrorist
<hw>Ter"ror*ist</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>terroriste</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who governs by
terrorism or intimidation; specifically, an agent or partisan of the
revolutionary tribunal during the Reign of Terror in France.</def>
<rj><au>Burke.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who commits terrorism{2}.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Terrorize</ent>⟦br⟧
